libebur128
------------------------------------------
libebur128 is a library that implements the EBU R 128 standard for loudness
normalisation.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libebur128-devel-1.2.6-1bl2
  libebur128_1-1.2.6-1bl2
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/jiixyj/libebur128

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/jiixyj/libebur128/archive/refs/tags/v1.2.6.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libebur128-1.2.6-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libebur128-1.2.6-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libebur128-1.2.6-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libebur128-1.2.6-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libebur128_1-1.2.6-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libebur128-devel-1.2.6-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libebur128)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libebur128.README
  /usr/share/doc/libebur128/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libebur128/R128Scan.txt
  /usr/share/doc/libebur128/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/libebur128/queue.txt

(libebur128_1)
  /usr/bin/cygebur128-1.dll

(libebur128-devel)
  /usr/include/ebur128.h
  /usr/lib/libebur128.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libebur128.pc

